high_descs: Turn to the left and move around the kitchen island, going past the range and dishwasher, then turn right and face the kitchen island.
Pick up the white mug closest to the edge and to the left of the loaf of bread from the kitchen island.
Turn right, move around the kitchen island and face the range.
Open the microwave above the range, place the mug in the microwave in front of the egg, microwave the mug, pick up the mug from the microwave and then close the microwave door.
Turn to the right, move past the sink and dishwasher, then turn to the left and face the blue coffee maker located between the wine bottle and the red toaster.
Place the mug in the coffee maker directly underneath the nozzle.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug in the coffee maker.

high_descs: Move to the other side of the island across from the dishwasher.
Pick up the coffee mug closest to the edge of the island.
Turn to the right and move to the microwave above the stove.
Put the mug in the microwave to the left of the bowl, warm it for a few seconds and take it back out.
Turn around and move towards the coffee maker on the left.
Put the coffee mug under the spout on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put the warmed coffee mug under the coffee maker spout.

high_descs: Walk around to face the opposite side of the table.
Pick up the cup on the table.
Turn right and walk forward to face the microwave above the stove.
Heat the cup in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and walk to the end of the left counter and turn turn left to face the coffee maker.
Place the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: To move a cup from the table to the coffee maker.
